

=Bio=

 
Advisor on economic policy for DIE LINKE (Left Party) in the German Bundestag. Latest publications: Exit not Exitus: The Red Project for Green Transformation in 16 Theses (Rosa Luxemburg Foundation, Policy Paper 03 / 2011). Towards Energy Democracy: The Current State of Germany’s Energy Transition (Trade Unions for Energy Democracy, Newsletter 01/2013). Forthcoming book: Thie, Hans (2013). Rotes Grün. Pioniere und Prinzipien einer ökologischen Gesellschaft. Hamburg: VSA-Verlag


